window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Spinster, sweet Spinster...</p> <p>Isabella Lambert is a nice person. She is biddable, polite, soft-spoken, and eager to please. She also happens to be a spinster, and one of the writers of the infamous Spinster Chronicles, where she is less polite, more outspoken, and may not please anyone. Izzy also has a secret that only one person knows, and that one person may hold the key to its success. </p> <p>Sebastian Morton finds Izzy Lambert fascinating. She is the perfect mentor for his younger sister, as well as a capable and charming friend for him. When opportunity strikes to spend more time with her, her secret becomes his. But will this secret, and others, ruin their connection?</p>"; 
